Hi all! *<!here>* :alarm: Plugging our feedback survey on Search internal preview once more! Please give us your thoughts before you head out for the holidays! :ty_thankyou:

Our Internal Preview for AI Hub Search has now been live for several months, and we want to hear about your experience using the product so far!

*Our Ask: Please submit your (honest) feedback via this Survey (https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf-nVzCwlt139H7DWKKmsm0nI8XdVfoIA9oXNvfDUlkY2dGbw/viewform) by Dec 20.*

Your input will help to inform our future product direction, and data enhancements to our own instance - thank you in advance!
